bandhavera varta yena jijnase bandhave
''kaha bandhu-saba, ki kusale ache sabe?''',NULL,NULL),('cb.antya.9.112','cb','cb.antya.9','ЧБ Антья 9.112',112,NULL,'''kusala'' sabdera artha vyakta karibare ‘bкаkti ache'' kаri'' varta layena sabare
bhavatsu kusala-prasna atmaramesu nesyate
kusalakusala yatra na santi mati-vrttayah
aty uttamanam kusala prasno loka-sukhecchaya nityadapta-sukhatvat tu na tesam yujyate kvacit
lokanam sukha-kartrtvam apeksya kusalam vibhoh prcchyate satatanandat katham tasyeva prcchyate
nanv addha mayi kurvanti kusalah svartha-darsinah
ahaituky avyavahitam bhaktim atma-priye yatha
yasyasti bhaktir bhagavaty akincana sarvair gunais tatra samasate surah harav abhaktasya kuto mahad-guna
mano-rathenasati dhavato bahih',NULL,NULL),('cb.antya.9.113','cb','cb.antya.9','ЧБ Антья 9.113',113,NULL,'bhakti-yoga thake, tabe sakala kusala bhakti vina raja haile о amangala
avismrtih krsna-padaravindayoh
ksinoty abhadrani ca sam tanoti
sattvasya suddhim paramatma-bhaktim jnanam ca vijnana-viraga-yuktam
yas tuttamah-sloka-gunanuvadah
sangiyate bhiksnam amangala-ghnah tam eva nityam srnuyad abhiksnam krsne ''malam bhaktim abhipsamanah
kuto ''sivam tvac-caranambujasavam
mahan-manasto mukha-nihsrtam kvacit pibanti ye karna-putair alam prabho deham-bhrtam deha-krd-asmrti-cchidam
ekah prapadyate dhvantam hitvedam sva-kalevaram kusaletara-patheyo bhuta-drohena yad bhrtam
rajyaisvarya-madonnaddho na sreyo vindate nrpah
tvan-maya-mohito ''nitya manyate sampado ''calah',NULL,NULL),('cb.antya.9.114','cb','cb.antya.9','ЧБ Антья 9.114',114,NULL,'dhana yasa bhoga yara achaye sakala
bhakti yara nai, tara saba amangala
sukhaya karmani karoti loko
na taih sukham vanyad-uparamam va vindeta bhuyas tata eva duhkham yad atra yuktam bhagavan vaden nah
sarve vedas ca yajnas ca tapo danani canagha
jlvabhaya-pradanasya na kurviran kalam api
yathaihikamusmika-kama-lampatah sutesu daresu dhanesu cintayan
sanketa vidvan kukalevaratyayad yas tasya yatnah srama eva kevalam',NULL,NULL),('cb.antya.9.115','cb','cb.antya.9','ЧБ Антья 9.115',115,NULL,'adya-khadya nahi yara—daridrera anta visnu-bhakti thakile, se-i se dhanavanta
namo ''kincana-vittaya nivrtta-guna-vrttaye atmaramaya santaya kaivalya-pataye namah',NULL,NULL),('cb.antya.9.116','cb','cb.antya.9','ЧБ Антья 9.116',116,NULL,'bhiksa-nimantrana-chale prabhu saba''-sthane vyakta kari'' iha kariyachena apane',NULL,NULL),('cb.antya.9.117','cb','cb.antya.9','ЧБ Антья 9.117',117,NULL,'bhiksa-nimantrane prabhu balena hasiya
"cala tumi age laksesvara hao giya',NULL,NULL),('cb.antya.9.118','cb','cb.antya.9','ЧБ Антья 9.118',118,NULL,'tatha bhiksa amara, ye haya laksesvara"
suniya brahmana saba cintita-antara',NULL,NULL),('cb.antya.9.119','cb','cb.antya.9','ЧБ Антья 9.119',119,NULL,'vipra-gana stuti kari'' balena "gosani laksera ki daya, sahasreko karo nai',NULL,NULL),('cb.antya.9.120','cb','cb.antya.9','ЧБ Антья 9.120',120,NULL,'tumi na karile bhiksa, garhasthya amara ekhanei pudiya hauk charakhara"',NULL,NULL),('cb.antya.9.121','cb','cb.antya.9','ЧБ Антья 9.121',121,NULL,'prabhu bale,—"jana, ''laksesvara'' bali kare? prati-dina laksa-nama ye grahana kare',NULL,NULL),('cb.antya.9.122','cb','cb.antya.9','ЧБ Антья 9.122',122,NULL,'se janera nama ami bali ''laksesvara'' tatha bhiksa amara, na yai anya ghara"',NULL,NULL),('cb.antya.9.123','cb','cb.antya.9','ЧБ Антья 9.123',123,NULL,'suniya prabhura krpa-vakya vipra-gane cinta chadi'' mahananda haila mane mane',NULL,NULL),('cb.antya.9.124','cb','cb.antya.9','ЧБ Антья 9.124',124,NULL,'"laksa nama laiba prabhu, tumi kara bhiksa mahabhagya,—e-mata karao tumi siksa"',NULL,NULL),('cb.antya.9.125','cb','cb.antya.9','ЧБ Антья 9.125',125,NULL,'prati-dina laksa nama sarva-dvija-gane layena caitanyacandra bhiksara karane',NULL,NULL),('cb.antya.9.126','cb','cb.antya.9','ЧБ Антья 9.126',126,NULL,'hena-mate bhakti-yoga laoyaya isvare vaikuntha-nayaka bhakti-sagare vihare',NULL,NULL),('cb.antya.9.127','cb','cb.antya.9','ЧБ Антья 9.127',127,NULL,'bhakti laoyaite sri-caitanya-avatara bhakti vina jijnasa na kare prabhu ara',NULL,NULL),('cb.antya.9.128','cb','cb.antya.9','ЧБ Антья 9.128',128,NULL,'prabhu bale,—"ye-janera krsna-bhakti ache
