nayam sukhapo bhagavan dehinam gopika-sutah jnaninam catma-bhutanam yatha bhaktimatam iha',NULL,NULL),('cb.antya.9.134','cb','cb.antya.9','ЧБ Антья 9.134',134,NULL,'prabhu bale,—"jnana haite bhakti bada kene?
