nasav rsir yasya matam na bhinnam dharmasya tattvam nihitam guhayam mahajano yena gatah sa panthah',NULL,NULL),('cb.antya.9.136','cb','cb.antya.9','ЧБ Антья 9.136',136,NULL,'veda-sastre mahajana-patha se laoyaya
